&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;We’re looking for an IT Support Engineer to provide hands-on technical support across our offices and help keep Gatik’s IT systems running smoothly day to day. This person will support employees with hardware, software, networking, and workplace technology needs, while helping maintain a reliable and secure IT environment. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;This is a highly tactical, onsite role ideal for someone who enjoys solving problems quickly, supporting end users, and working across a wide range of IT systems and tools.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;This role is onsite 5 days/week at our Santa Clara, CA office!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;What you&#39;ll do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
