&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: &#39;times new roman&#39;, times, serif;&quot;&gt;Set up and configure new hire equipment, user accounts, access permissions, and software&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
